{"tid":1813871,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"如果TVB肯跪，大家會開咩條件？","createTime":"2020-01-06T14:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T16:52:01.000Z","uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"9b34fcbbc9dc77a1e35a23575731dbbf1ddc1327","tid":1813871,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:42:14.000Z","msg":"以前奶共就話爽，宜家黃圈係本港力量咁大，係人都睇得出TVB無法抗衡。<br />\n<br />\n唔通為左保一個袁花搞到執笠，比後代恥笑千百年？<br />\n<br />\n雖然TVB表面一副死不悔改嘅7樣，但蝕到入肉都咪話唔肉痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTVB可能都有半隻腳想跪，只係腦筋不思轉彎咁多年未知點做，不妨幫佢諗下。"},{"pid":"05e671917bdf419400979f729cf649824f30930b","tid":1813871,"uid":15823,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:51:12.000Z","msg":"真無法抗衡既話唔該摺左先講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed375511c41a1fe89d3f07dd75636bb9f0ddcce","tid":1813871,"uid":127177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:56:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />精神勝利法？"},{"pid":"47548448ea6521a5042886240e9f8723865c8c9c","tid":1813871,"uid":72863,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T15:00:24.000Z","msg":"執左佢！"},{"pid":"90322c61f07b2053370a65f7d993caee4f62e51f","tid":1813871,"uid":44277,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T15:01:48.000Z","msg":"6點半新聞之前首支共歌CANCEL, 改播榮光"},{"pid":"211fd11d6103b4af90dbc74877c8477267d874cf","tid":1813871,"uid":3028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T15:02:32.000Z","msg":"免費播英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5e0b494dfa4214f5c1b0fb8b3501d8683b4474","tid":1813871,"uid":124690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T15:03:42.000Z","msg":"清盤"},{"pid":"bb03f0eb5710b8ebfdd9a35c224b887797b511f8","tid":1813871,"uid":1524,"like"